      <S N="Description">A module for lifecycle management of the Microsoft Visual C++ Redistributables. VcRedist downloads, installs and uninstalls the supported (and unsupported) Redistributables. Use for local install, gold image creation and update, or importing as applications into the Microsoft Deployment Toolkit, Microsoft Configuration Manager or Microsoft Intune. Supports passive and silent installs, and uninstalls of the Visual C++ Redistributables.</S>
